# EmailJS credentials for the contact form (src/App.vue).
# Get these from https://www.emailjs.com after creating a free account:
# 1. Email Services -> Add New Service (connect Gmail) -> copy the Service ID
# 2. Email Templates -> create a template with variables matching the ones
#    sent from submitContactForm (name, email, phone, website, about,
#    interests, budget, timeline, referral, comments) -> copy the Template ID
# 3. Account -> General -> copy the Public Key
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=
